Cell["\<\
This demonstrates supervised learning  using topological associative memory.
Raw images have been preprocessed with Gaussian blur.
Image data is encoded as sparse distributed representations (SDRs), using  a \
random sparse projection followed by k-winners-take-all.
We encode labels as non-overlapping random sparse holographic representations \
(SHRs).
\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"86cc569a-be37-4aff-8a57-73ac76739a7f"],

